CS2 CONSOLE STATS is a professional desktop application for Counter-Strike 2 players that provides real-time match statistics, advanced performance analytics, and comprehensive historical data tracking. Unlike web-based trackers, this EXE software runs locally on your machine, pulling data directly from Steam API and local demo files for instant, private, and detailed stat analysis without uploading your data to third-party servers. [citation:1][citation:5][citation:7]

