📥 DOWNLOAD & INSTALLATION INSTRUCTIONS

STEP 1: Download the ZIP file from the link above
STEP 2: Right-click the downloaded ZIP → Extract All
STEP 3: Choose a destination folder (C:\CS2_Stats or Desktop recommended)
STEP 4: Open the extracted folder
STEP 5: Double-click .exe to launch
STEP 6: Log in with your Steam account (secure local authentication)
STEP 7: Start tracking your matches automatically

⚠ NOTE: Windows SmartScreen may show warning - click "More info" then "Run anyway"

