✨ KEY FEATURES

• Real-time match tracking — live stats during active CS2 matches [citation:5]
• Premier rank & ELO tracking — monitor your rank progression over time
• Advanced performance metrics — ADR, HS%, KAST, Rating 2.0, and more [citation:5][citation:9]
• Weapon-specific analytics — accuracy, kills, headshot percentage per weapon
• Demo file analysis — parse local .dem files for deep tactical insights [citation:2][citation:6][citation:9]
• Heatmap generation — visualize your positioning and kill zones
• Session history — track all matches in current gaming session
• Enemy stats — see detailed performance of opponents you face
• Export capabilities — save stats as CSV, JSON, or PDF reports [citation:2]
• Steam integration — secure local authentication, no cloud upload [citation:3]
• Offline mode — analyze demos without internet connection
• FACEIT sync — optional integration for FACEIT match stats [citation:5][citation:10]

