🔧 HOW TO USE

LIVE MATCH TRACKING
────────────────────
1. Launch CS2 Console Stats EXE
2. Log in with Steam (secure local auth)
3. Launch CS2 and start playing
4. Stats appear automatically in real-time
5. Press F9 during match for quick overlay

DEMO ANALYSIS
────────────────────
1. Download your CS2 demo files (.dem)
2. Place them in the "demos" folder inside installation directory
3. Click "Import Demo" in the application
4. Select demo file for detailed analysis
5. View round-by-round breakdowns and heatmaps [citation:2][citation:6][citation:9]

HISTORICAL TRACKING
────────────────────
1. Application automatically syncs with Steam match history
2. View last 20+ matches with full statistics
3. Track progress over days, weeks, months
4. Compare performance across different maps

EXPORT REPORTS
────────────────────
1. Select matches or session to export
2. Choose format (CSV, JSON, PDF)
3. Click "Export" to save report
4. Share with coaches or teammates [citation:2]

