📄 README.TXT (extracted from ZIP)

==================================================
CS2 CONSOLE STATS v2.4.0
==================================================

Thank you for downloading CS2 Console Stats!

This professional tool provides comprehensive
statistics and analytics for Counter-Strike 2 players.

QUICK START:
────────────────
1. Extract ALL files from this ZIP archive
2. Run .exe
3. Click "Login with Steam" (secure local auth)
4. Launch CS2 and start playing
5. Stats appear automatically!

FEATURES:
────────────────
• Live match tracking with real-time updates
• Premier rank and ELO monitoring
• Advanced metrics (ADR, HS%, Rating, KAST)
• Weapon-specific performance analytics
• Demo file analysis for deep tactical review
• Session history and export capabilities
• Heatmap generation for positioning analysis

HOTKEYS:
────────────────
F9  - Toggle overlay during match
F10 - Quick stats snapshot
F11 - Export current match data
F12 - Screenshot stats window

TROUBLESHOOTING:
────────────────
• If Steam login fails, ensure Steam client is running
• If stats don't appear, check "Auto-refresh" in settings
• For demo analysis, place .dem files in /demos folder
• Windows Defender: Add folder exclusion if needed

VERSION: 2.4.0
RELEASE: March 2026

==================================================

